Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证会的\NYeah, I'll make sure to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.08,0:22:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  没事了  再见\NOkay. Alright, bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.21,0:22:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你  周日见\NLove you! See you Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你得保证他不会遇上麻烦尼克\NMake sure he stays out of trouble, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-没问题  -再见\N- Will do. - bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.06,0:23:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧\NOh, let's get the fuck out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.73,0:23:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我不懂你们怎么做到的\NI don't know how you guys do it, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.20,0:23:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么是烈酒解决不了的\NHard liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.06,0:23:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们这不招待你们 -  是吗  那是啥\N- We don't serve your kind here. - Oh, yeah? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.87,0:23:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,聪明  帅气的男人\NSmart, handsome men?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.34,0:23:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,只有男人是事实\NYou got the "men" part right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.10,0:23:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,进展如何  伙计  我的小木屋怎么样\NHow's it going, buddy? How's my cabin coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.12,0:24:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道  我们到了就知道了\NI don't know. I guess we'll see it when we get up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.91,0:24:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,混的怎么样\NHow's it hanging, Sal?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.24,0:24:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,还行\NSouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.05,0:24:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一如既往  不过没以前那么好了\NAs always, man. Just don't get up like it used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.28,0:24:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,对  我听说了\NYeah, I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.32,0:24:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,两位女士喝什么\NWhat are you ladies drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.62,0:24:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,凉的就行\NOh, anything cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.69,0:24:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,请你们\NOn the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.69,0:24:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好\NHear, hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.06,0:24:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NAppreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.86,0:24:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,塔拉最近还好吧\NHow Tara doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.30,0:24:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  她  她挺好的\NYeah, she's... she's doing alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.84,0:24:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一直挺忙\NKeeping busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.14,0:24:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-你呢  -我挺好\N- How you doing? - I'm alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.94,0:24:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你那电话还在吗\NYou still got a phone back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.81,0:24:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  就在后面\NYeah, come on back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.35,0:24:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,代我向塔拉问好\NTell Tara I said "hello."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.82,0:24:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NWill do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.21,0:25:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  亲爱的\NUh, hey, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.38,0:25:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是我  我们  我们刚到乔丹那\NIt's me. We just, uh... just got to Jordan's.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.95,0:25:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们马上去小木屋\NWe're about to head out to the cabin in a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.31,0:25:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你在哪  我\NNot sure where you are. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.22,0:25:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-尼克  -塔拉\N- Nick. - Tara?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.32,0:25:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  不好意思  我刚在洗澡\NHey, sorry. I was in the shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.69,0:25:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到电话铃响了\NI heard the machine cut on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.06,0:25:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没事儿\NIt's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.86,0:25:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们才到这一会儿\NYeah, we just made it out here a little bit ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.79,0:25:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在乔丹这喝两杯\NJust sitting at Jordan's having a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.83,0:25:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\Noh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.70,0:25:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,喝两杯\NHaving a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.83,0:25:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上小心点\NYou be careful in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.80,0:25:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,特别是在路上开车\NEspecially on those roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.70,0:25:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI will.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.40,0:25:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃晚饭了吗\NYou eat dinner yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.21,0:25:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,吃了\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.94,0:25:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,把乳蛋饼吃完了\NFinished the quiche.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.31,0:25:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,乔丹向你问好\NJordan says "hi."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.01,0:25:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他真好  跟他说我也向他问好\NThat's sweet. You tell him I said "hi" back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.28,0:25:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我会的\NYeah, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.54,0:25:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那是啥\NWhat was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.32,0:25:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  我在做派\NOh, I'm making a pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.82,0:25:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.09,0:25:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,万一玛琳来了呢\NIn case Marlene comes by.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.36,0:26:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,说曹操曹操到\NSpeak of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.10,0:26:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了\NI gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.13,0:26:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NAlright.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.00,0:26:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-我爱你  -嗯  我也爱你\N- I love you. - Yeah, I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.17,0:26:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我来啦\NI'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.74,0:26:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,等一小会  玛琳\NHold on a god damn moment, Marlene.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.92,0:26:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你们分了没\NHey, man, she left you yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.25,0:26:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有告诉她我和她打招呼了\NYou tell her I said "hello"?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.96,0:26:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NYep.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.29,0:26:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她也和你打招呼了\NShe said "hi" back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.26,0:26:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有告诉她我说嗨\NYou tell her I said "hi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.96,0:26:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没\NHell no.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.78,0:28:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.12,0:28:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你知道我不问你也会和我说的\NHey, man, you'd think I wouldn't have to ask. You know you will tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.86,0:28:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这个玩意\NThis shit, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.09,0:28:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那个疤挺大的  看着都疼\NThat's a big mother fucker, man. Looks like it hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.20,0:28:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,特别大的那种\NBig-ass scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.64,0:28:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一直到屁股那\NFell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.24,0:28:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,去你的\NFuck you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.54,0:28:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.94,0:29:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不过  嘿  我认真的\NHey, I'm serious, though, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.18,0:29:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是和一帮错误的人鬼混了一段时间\NI was just hanging out with the wrong guys for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.62,0:29:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人有点像那种\NWe were sort of like a...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.49,0:29:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我不知道你会怎么看他们\NI… I don't know what you call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.29,0:29:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不是什么好的  这是肯定的\NDidn't add up to anything good, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.76,0:29:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就用这种回答打发我了\NThe fuck kind of answer is that, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.30,0:29:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸和乔丹退到幕后很久了\NMy dad and Jordan went back quite a ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.24,0:29:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是他把我介绍给了朱尼尔\Nand he's the one that introduced me to Junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.42,0:29:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉最好要\NI figured it was better to, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.98,0:29:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,最好找个我认识几个人的地方重新开始\Nstart new somewhere where I knew a couple people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.32,0:29:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我遇见了塔拉\NThen I met Tara.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.69,0:29:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样  一切就结束了\NThat was it. That sealed the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.92,0:29:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你和她结婚结对了  兄弟\NYou married right with that one, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.98,0:30:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说至少你岳父\NI mean, at least your father-in-law
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.20,0:30:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可以免你的罚单\Ncan get you out of tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.06,0:30:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我岳父只会打得我满地找牙\NMine just kicks me in the teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.20,0:30:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  这点上咱们挺像\NYeah, well, we got something in common on that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.72,0:30:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-来一瓶吗  -嗯\N- Want one? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.49,0:30:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有一个  你知道吗\NI got one, too, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.66,0:30:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.56,0:30:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这个  看到了吗  就在那\NCheck that out. See that right there?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.19,0:30:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  天  你哪搞来的\NOh, shit. Where'd you pick that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.66,0:30:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-玛琳  -玛琳\N- Marlene. - Marlene?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.13,0:30:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,其实是她前夫\NActually, that was her ex-husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.20,0:30:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说其实  那个时候是她丈夫\NI mean, technically, it was her husband at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.07,0:30:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  你搅黄了人家婚姻\NWait. So you broke up a marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.11,0:30:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不是  不是  等等\NNo, no, no. Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.58,0:30:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那样\NWasn't like that, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.26,0:30:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他们那时已经在离婚边缘了\NShe had one foot out of the door already.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.11,0:30:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那天她来到室内装潢店\NWhen she came in the upholstery store,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.75,0:30:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,问她的躺椅做好了没\Nasked to have her recliner done,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.09,0:30:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就那样散发她的魅惑能量  伙计\Nshe was just radiating that energy she has, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.52,0:30:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我就沦陷了  兄弟  看了她一眼就这样\NI was done, man. Took one look at her. That was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.18,0:31:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  现在想想\NOf course, now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.33,0:31:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在她离婚之前就把她肚子搞大了\Ngetting her pregnant before she was divorced
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.16,0:31:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是有点过  但是\Nprobably sped some things up a little bit, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.73,0:31:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他一点不友好  那天他走进来\NHe didn't take too kindly to that, and he came in
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.77,0:31:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,用拆轮胎的棒子照着我头打\Nand hit me in the head with a tire iron one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.34,0:31:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,对  我昏迷了20分钟\NYeah, yeah. I was out for 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.01,0:31:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,醒过来  大约缝了15针\NWoke up. About 15 stitches and...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.01,0:31:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,该死  有点记不全了\NNo shit. I don't really remember much,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.35,0:31:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你问我  我会说挺惨的\Nbut it's kinda fucked up, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.86,0:31:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,玛琳和我几个礼拜以后就结婚了\NMarlene and I got married a few weeks later.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.06,0:31:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,然后她就一直在我身边\NAnd she's been around ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.52,0:31:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那她那个丈夫呢\NWhat happened to the husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.70,0:31:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他被关了大概4个月\NHe went inside for about four months.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.10,0:31:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上在监狱结婚了\NGot married in prison, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.80,0:31:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我也没感觉特别对不起他\NSo I don't feel too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.74,0:31:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  伙计\NHey, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.67,0:31:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喝酒  致敬那个把你揍扁\NHere's to finding the one that'll fuck you rotten
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.38,0:31:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,然后给你烧早饭的女人\Nand then cook you breakfast afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.25,0:31:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她把你揍扁了吗\NShe fucks you rotten, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.81,0:31:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,也不算吧  伙计  但也差不多了\NNo, not really, man, but one out of two ain't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.52,0:31:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.46,0:33:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,下午好\NAfternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.87,0:33:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样了\NHow's it coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.88,0:34:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还需要一个周末  但就快了\NWe're gonna need another weekend at it, but it's coming along.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.48,0:34:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-你拿的什么  -几十块钱的大麻\N- What you got there? - Popped a couple doves.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.88,0:34:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你可能想抽点\NI thought you might want to smoke some.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.22,0:34:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  伙计\NOh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.78,0:34:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你真了解我\NSpeaking to my soul now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.70,0:34:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  我能再用一下你的电话吗\NHey, can I use your phone again?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.22,0:34:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊  没问题  来吧\NYeah, of course. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.71,0:35:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我要棉花糖\NI want marshmallows!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.45,0:35:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再吃棉花糖了\NNo more marshmallows for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.45,0:35:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-糖分太高了  -就一块\N- It's too much sugar. - Just one?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.42,0:35:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  小姐  你不能\NNo, ma'am. You are not...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.52,0:35:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  这里是伯特家\NHi. You've reached the Porters.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.76,0:35:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在没在家\NWe're not home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.29,0:35:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要留言的话\NSo if you could please leave a message,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.89,0:35:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回来立刻就联系你  好吗\Nwe'll get back to you as soon as possible. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.63,0:35:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  尼克\NHey, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.89,0:35:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,过来兄弟  妈的\NCome on, man. Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.80,0:35:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是迟到了玛琳一定会弄死我\NMarlene's gonna whup my ass if I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.60,0:35:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,快点兄弟  该走了\NCome on, man. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.50,0:35:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好  是啊我们上路吧\NYeah. Yeah, let's hit the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.32,0:35:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这才对\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.94,0:35:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚给你家打了电话\NI just called your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.88,0:35:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没人接\NNobody answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.78,0:35:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没人吗\NNo?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.14,0:35:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没人接吗\NNobody?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.98,0:35:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,通常这个时间她应该在给他们洗澡\NWell, she usually gives them a bath right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.94,0:35:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢  说不定想淹死他们\NWho knows? Maybe she's drowning them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.00,0:35:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定在分尸\NMight have finally cracked.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.36,0:36:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好了兄弟  明天一早\NAlright, man. Tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.69,0:36:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NYup.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.60,0:38:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-该死的  -把枪放下  尼克\N- Damn it! - Put it down, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.03,0:38:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的  把枪放下\NFuck! Put it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.67,0:38:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他开枪打我\NHe shot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.20,0:38:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-妈的  -是他干的\N- Fuck. - He did.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.77,0:39:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,把枪放下\NPut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.34,0:39:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,把枪放下\NPut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.91,0:39:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\NNick.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.14,0:39:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,操\NFuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.91,0:39:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她先利用我们的  尼克\NShe drew on us first, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.05,0:39:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,确实如此\NIt's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.75,0:39:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,放松一点  孩子\NJust take a load off, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.21,0:39:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那是伤了我的心的代价\NThat's for breaking my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.36,0:39:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,还有查理的一份\NAnd Charlie's.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.56,0:39:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不过现在来看那都是过去的事了  很\NAh, but that's in the past now. It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.06,0:39:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,见到你很高兴  尼克\NIt is so good to see you, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.60,0:39:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但我有个问题要问你\NI got a question for you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.90,0:40:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你有冰淇淋吗\NYou got any ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.64,0:40:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  一开始  当我们进来的时候\NI mean, initially, when we came in,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.11,0:40:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那个小姑娘  那位女士正在做馅饼\Nthe little lady, the missus was making a pie,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.11,0:40:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把它放回冰箱里\Nand we got it back in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.64,0:40:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  那听起来是不是很合理\NI mean, doesn't that sound normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.28,0:40:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,馅饼和冰淇淋\NPie and ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.82,0:40:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,对呢\NYep.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.96,0:40:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有奶油胡桃味的\NYou wouldn't happen to have any butter pecan, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.59,0:40:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\NNick?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.26,0:40:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看他有没有冰淇淋\NGo see if he's got any ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.46,0:40:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,认真的吗  我他妈还在这流血呢\NSeriously? I'm fucking bleeding out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.07,0:40:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我得看着这个\NI gotta get this looked at.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.61,0:40:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为你需要做什么\NWhat'd you think you were gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.74,0:40:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算戴上个面具\NYou were gonna put on a mask
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.81,0:40:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,让别人相信你很正常是吗\Nand make believe you were normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.18,0:40:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是这么想的\NIt wasn't gonna catch up to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.60,0:41:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你杀了她\NYou killed her
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.60,0:41:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就在你把戒指戴在她小拇指的那一刻\Nthe minute you put that ring on her little finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.71,0:41:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有点讽刺不是吗  查理\NIt's kind of ironic, isn't it, Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.24,0:41:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我也这么想的  没错\NThat's what I'd call it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.28,0:41:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,尼古拉斯\NNicholas...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.88,0:41:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是你唯一的家人\N...we're the only family you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.15,0:41:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是唯一能够真正理解你\NWe're the only ones who will ever understand you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.29,0:41:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你本来的样子\Nfor what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.03,0:41:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们他妈是一家啊\NWe were a fucking family.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.70,0:41:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,而你却想杀了我们\NAnd you tried to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.04,0:41:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很搞笑\NIt's actually pretty funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.77,0:41:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还真有奶油胡桃味\NThey actually have butter pecan.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.41,0:41:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  嘿布鲁斯\NHey, hey, Bruce...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.81,0:41:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\NShut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.96,0:42:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们第一次来这的时候  兄弟\NWhen we first showed up, man,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.32,0:42:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这待了  多久  两天吧\Nwe were here for, what, two days?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.89,0:42:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这  聊天  聊关于\NWe were here, talking. Talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.00,0:42:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,天气\Nabout the weather
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.70,0:42:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,还和那个小姑娘塔拉聊各种屁事\Nand all kinds of shit with the little lady, with Tara.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.77,0:42:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫塔拉对吧\NTara is her name, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.24,0:42:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,活着时候是的\NWas her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.04,0:42:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟你真应该看看她死前的样子\NMan, you should've seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.14,0:42:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,她叨叨叨个没完  兄弟\NShe wouldn't shut the fuck up, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.94,0:42:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,问我们各种各样的问题\NShe was asking us all kinds of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.31,0:42:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇心十足\NReal inquisitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.68,0:42:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,然后她告诉我们钱的事\NAnd then she told us about the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.15,0:42:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,想象一下  她告诉我们你说你\NImagine that. She told us that you said that you, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.79,0:42:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你继承了这笔钱\Nyou inherited the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.43,0:42:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,谁他妈的会让你继承遗产呢\NWho the fuck is leaving you any money?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.46,0:42:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会对妻子说这样的谎\NWho does that to their wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.86,0:42:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,什么人会那样欺骗他们的妻子\NWho lies to their wife like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.10,0:42:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什么样的人会做出那种事  尼克\NWhat kind of man does that, Nick?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.77,0:42:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是用我们的钱买下这个地方的尼克\NDid you use our money to buy this place, Nick?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.77,0:42:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她是这么告诉我们的\NBecause that's what she told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.11,0:42:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\NShit.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.98,0:43:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓\NDoesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.38,0:43:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,都无所谓了\NDoesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.39,0:43:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你就应该他妈的冲着我们来\NYou should've just fucking come to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.22,0:43:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,操你妈的布鲁斯\NGod damn it, Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.23,0:43:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他他妈朝他冲过去了啊\NFucking lunged at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.73,0:43:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他朝你冲过去了\NHe lunged at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.00,0:43:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\NNick.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.16,0:43:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哦妈的\NOh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.14,0:43:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\NNick.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.91,0:43:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  尼克  尼克  尼克\NNick, Nick, Nick, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.84,0:43:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  孩子\NNow, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.45,0:43:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我想这就是传说中的解脱\N...I guess this is what you'd call closure.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.98,0:44:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  对不起\NNick, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.53,0:46:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋\NBastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.25,0:46:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  快点\NCome on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.42,0:46:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.08,0:48:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱动\NDon't struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.12,0:48:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这多久了\NHow long have I been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.26,0:48:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你是个麻烦  尼克\NI always knew you were trouble, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.00,0:48:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不应该离开\NI shouldn't have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.42,0:49:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诫过你离我女儿远点\NI told you to stay away from my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.80,0:49:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,结果却相反\NBut you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.55,0:49:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉她不要嫁给你  又事与愿违\NTold her not to marry you, but she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.79,0:49:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她说我没有她了解你\NSaid I didn't know you like she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.24,0:49:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但我却再清楚不过你是什么人  不是吗\NBut I knew exactly what you were, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.40,0:49:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在坐在这里\NNow I'm sitting here...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.54,0:49:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,想着\N...wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.48,0:49:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么没拿出我的枪然后直接\N...why I shouldn't take my gun and just...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.32,0:49:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这是谁干的\NWho do you think did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.93,0:49:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,别逼我尼克\NDon't push me, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.59,0:49:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你得让我走\NYou gotta let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.23,0:49:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我会放你走\NYou think I would do something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.57,0:50:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你和萨尔一起捕猎\NI know you were hunting with Sal.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.91,0:50:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,验尸官告诉我\NThe coroner told me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.71,0:50:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经死了两天了\N...that she'd been dead for two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.45,0:50:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道不是你杀的她\NI know you didn't pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.69,0:50:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但你知道是谁干的\NBut you know who did.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.59,0:50:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗\NDon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.83,0:50:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.57,0:50:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你让我走  我会处理的\NAnd I'll handle it if you let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.64,0:50:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那一套在这是行不通的  孩子\NWell, that's not the way we do things around here, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.99,0:51:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里\NWhere you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.29,0:51:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点事不能在这\NI can't be here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.26,0:51:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他一醒你就要通知我\NBut you let me know the second he wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.24,0:51:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-好的  为什么  -布拉德\N- Sure. Why would... - Brad.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.40,0:51:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不久就会回来\NI'll be back in a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.77,0:51:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在  你要像只老鹰一样盯着他\NBut for now, you just watch him like a fucking hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.12,0:54:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看看呐\NWell, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.66,0:54:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他醒了\NHe's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.50,0:54:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,胸部感觉如何\NHow's your chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.17,0:55:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很疼  是吧\NHurts, don't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.08,0:55:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你介不介意\NWould you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.33,0:55:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.71,0:55:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,喝水\NDrink.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.45,0:55:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,口渴\NThirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.96,0:55:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.84,0:55:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOh, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.81,0:55:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吧\NHey, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.04,0:55:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\NHey, you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.54,0:55:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  尼克\NNick? Nick?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.00,0:59:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\NHow you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.50,0:59:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我去抽个烟\NI'm gonna go for a smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.89,0:59:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,萨尔\NSal.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.77,0:59:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\NI'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.52,0:59:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证\NPromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.36,0:59:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪  兄弟\NJesus fucking Christ, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.35,0:59:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\NNick?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.71,0:59:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事\NOh, what the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.08,0:59:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\NNick.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.77,0:59:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的发生了什么  兄弟\NWhat the fuck happened to you, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.79,0:59:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪来的\NWhere you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.09,0:59:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把我锁在医院里\NThey had me at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.77,0:59:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在医院\NIn the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.03,1:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的兄弟  我去了  然后\NNo, man. I went there, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.00,1:00:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,警察说你不在那里  兄弟\Ncop says you weren't there, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.43,1:00:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吧\NYou alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.17,1:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.04,1:00:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 该死的  兄弟  我很抱歉\NOh, shit, man. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.38,1:00:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说了塔拉的事\NI heard about Tara.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.05,1:00:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么听说的\NWhat'd you hear?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.50,1:00:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,人们在捏造是你杀了她  兄弟\NPeople be trying to say that you killed her, man,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.06,1:00:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但我知道那是胡扯的兄弟\Nbut I know that's bullshit, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.13,1:00:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  看着我  我知道那是胡说八道\NHey, look at me. I know that's bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.53,1:00:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道是谁干的吗\NYou know who did it?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.12,1:00:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是的我知道  我需要你的帮助\NYeah, I know. I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.27,1:00:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAlright.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.87,1:00:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你帮我藏好这辆车\NI need you to help me hide this car,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.44,1:00:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我还需要借一下你的面包车\Nand I need to borrow your van.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.32,1:00:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  好的\NYeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.11,1:00:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你需要  兄弟\NAnything you need, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.78,1:00:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-但我要和你一起去  -不\N- But I'm gonna go with you. - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.35,1:00:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能让你去  萨尔\NI can't let you do that, Sal.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.09,1:00:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能让你被牵连\NI can't let you get involved with this.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.02,1:00:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经被牵连了\NI'm already involved here.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.36,1:00:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我在我的院子里藏一辆警车\NYou're asking me to hide a police car in my yard.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.16,1:01:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-不  不  -嘿\N- No, no. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.26,1:01:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你  兄弟\NLook at you, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.83,1:01:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你单独去做这事\NI'm not letting you do this alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.04,1:01:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不如闭上嘴我们一起开始行动吧\NYou wanna stop talking about it and go do this thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.16,1:01:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢这样  萨尔\NI don't like this, Sal.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.26,1:01:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我一点也不喜欢这样\NI don't like this one bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.93,1:01:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们来问  记住该怎么说\NJust remember what to say if they come asking.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.60,1:01:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你不应该这么做\NI don't think you should do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.61,1:01:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他会为我们做同样的事  好吧\NHe'd do the same thing for us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.05,1:01:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很抱歉  尼克\NI'm really sorry, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.49,1:02:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,为我们留着灯\NLeave the light on for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.48,1:02:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,别让自己陷入麻烦  萨尔\NDon't get yourself in trouble, Sal.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.06,1:02:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-天杀的  -很抱歉  弗兰克\N- God damn it. - I'm sorry, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.14,1:02:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,天杀的\NGod damn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.34,1:02:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你回他的房子去\NYou get back over to his house.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.54,1:03:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,接近房子50米内的人全部逮捕\NYou arrest anybody that comes within 50 yards of that place.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.15,1:03:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你逮捕后马上通过对讲机通知我\NAnd you radio me right away if you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.92,1:03:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-明白了吗  -明白  长官\N- You got that? - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.46,1:03:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs17}旅行者休息汽车旅馆
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.95,1:03:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,别熄火\NKeep it running.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.66,1:04:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了  兄弟\NWhat's up, man?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.20,1:04:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  没有\NNothing? Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.11,1:04:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你想试试90号公路旁的那个地方吗\NYou wanna try that place off 90?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.08,1:04:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.46,1:04:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NYeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.52,1:04:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs17}公路汽车旅馆\NHBO有线电视  电影  电话
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.80,1:05:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下\NHold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.77,1:05:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么事吗\NMay I help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.24,1:05:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我找人\NI'm looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.72,1:05:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-谁  -他们是三个人\N- Someone? - Three men.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.34,1:05:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会在这里度过周末\NThey would have stayed here over the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.12,1:05:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,开着一辆绿色的凯迪拉克\NDriving a green Cadillac.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.52,1:05:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他们应该付的是现金\NThey would've paid in cash.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.12,1:05:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在102号房\NStayed in room 102.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.58,1:06:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你说你是谁呢\NWho'd you say you were?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.92,1:06:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,布拉德·安格斯\NBrad Engels.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.36,1:06:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,公安局的\NSheriff's department.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.74,1:06:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  让我快速查一下\NAlright, let me check real fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.38,1:06:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,102号房\N102.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.93,1:06:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,福特  沃尔特·福特\NFord. Walter Ford.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.19,1:06:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他给我的名字\NThat's the name he gave me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.23,1:06:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还在这里吗\NThey still here?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.86,1:06:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在这里待了几晚上\NThey were here a few nights.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.83,1:06:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来来去去有几次\NThey came and went a few times.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.98,1:06:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他们今天下午就离开了\NThey left this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.57,1:06:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你那间房租出去了吗\NYou rent out that room yet?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.00,1:06:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.52,1:06:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,让我进那间房\NLet me in that room.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.46,1:07:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样\NYeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.71,1:07:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.78,1:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,102号房\N102.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.02,1:08:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在找什么  兄弟\NWhat are we looking for, man?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.14,1:09:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.54,1:09:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他们早就走了\NYeah, I think they're long gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.49,1:09:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,所有单位  在公路汽车旅馆\NAll units, we have shots fired
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.76,1:09:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有枪击事件发生\Nat the Hiway Host Motel.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.88,1:09:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我是帕森\NThis is Parson.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.33,1:09:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,接到来自公路汽车旅馆的报警电话\NReceived a 911 call from the Hiway Host Motel.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.73,1:10:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,通话被打断  但线路还是通的\NCall did drop, but the line is still live.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.53,1:10:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,明白  马上去\N10-4. On my way.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.43,1:11:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\NJesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.66,1:12:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.80,1:12:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,查理\NCharlie?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.93,1:12:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  兄弟  你最好回休息站去\NHey, man, you better get back to the pit stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.00,1:12:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,斯隆准备出发了\NSloan's ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.46,1:14:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好  长官\NGood morning, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.12,1:14:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好  卡罗尔\NMorning, Carol.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.86,1:14:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好  本尼七点左右打了电话\NMorning. Benny called around 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.76,1:14:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,面包车有线索了吗\NAny sign of the van?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.66,1:15:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,实验室说他们需要几周时间才能\NLab said they wouldn't be able to pull the prints
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.23,1:15:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,从那辆大众开迪上取下指纹\Nfor a couple weeks off the Caddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.27,1:15:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,科尔顿县的小伙子们呢\NWhat about the boys in Colton County?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.14,1:15:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也没有\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.38,1:15:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,鼻子如何\NHow's the nose?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.26,1:15:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\NIt's... It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.34,1:15:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你如何呢\NHow you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.79,1:15:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在度过中\NI'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.13,1:15:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,咖啡已经煮好一个小时了\NCoffee's been on for about an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.05,1:15:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-公安局  -嘿  布拉德\N- Sheriff's department. - Hey, brad.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.38,1:15:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我是乔丹·穆雷\NIt's Jordan Murray.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.95,1:15:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我打电话是因为\NListen, I just wanted to call because...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.45,1:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我知道尼克·布伦纳在哪里\NI think I know where Nick Brenner is.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.85,1:16:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他之前在我的小屋干活\NHe was working on my cabin.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.89,1:16:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克  一号线有你的电话\NFrank, you got a call on line one.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.13,1:16:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你想接这个电话\NI think you might wanna pick this up.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.97,1:16:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我是弗兰克\NThis is Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.20,1:16:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克  我是乔丹·穆雷\NFrank, Jordan Murray here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.20,1:16:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚告诉布拉德\NI was just telling Brad
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.80,1:16:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我可能知道尼克·布伦纳在哪里\Nthat I think I might know where Nick Brenner is.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.60,1:16:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上来\NI'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.61,1:19:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他是谁\NWho was he?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.44,1:19:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只是一个人\NJust a man.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.92,1:19:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那你要告诉我这里发生了什么吗  尼克\NWell, you gonna tell me what happened here, Nick?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.10,1:20:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,至少那是我应该知道的\NI deserve that much at least.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.20,1:20:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在找什么  兄弟\NWhat are we looking for, man?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.48,1:20:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.48,1:20:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他们早就走了\NYeah, I think they're long gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.33,1:21:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,操\NFuck, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.68,1:21:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说\NI mean, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.07,1:21:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,操\NOh, fuck! Aah!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.44,1:21:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,萨尔\NSal?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.04,1:21:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\NGod!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.52,1:21:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,忘了这吧\NForget about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.19,1:21:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.79,1:21:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎么回事  -回去\N- What's going on? - Get back!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.43,1:21:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,操\NFuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.76,1:22:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你  看你干的好事\NYou! Look what you did!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.50,1:22:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-看你干的好事  -看着我\N- Look what you did! - Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.78,1:22:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该在那栋房子里就死掉的\NYou were supposed to die in that house.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.85,1:22:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有\NI didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.61,1:22:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我看得出来\NI can see that.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.35,1:22:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪里\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.52,1:22:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以再次成为家人\NWe could've been a family again.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.09,1:22:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,像以前一样\NLike before.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.50,1:22:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.63,1:22:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他在站里\NHe's at the station.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.67,1:22:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,什么站\NWhat station?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.14,1:22:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,卡车站\NTruck stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.11,1:23:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就沿着这条路走\NIt's just down the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.48,1:23:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,动手吧  尼克\NCome on, Nick!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.86,1:23:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,萨尔\NSal?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.57,1:23:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.14,1:23:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  哥们\NHey, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.71,1:23:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  萨尔\NHey. Sal.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.41,1:23:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我  醒醒  兄弟\NLook at me. Come on, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.18,1:23:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.78,1:23:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  糟糕\NOh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.62,1:23:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,操\NOh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.70,1:23:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.51,1:25:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.62,1:25:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,查理\NCharlie?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.72,1:25:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  兄弟  你最好回休息站去\NHey, man, you better get back to the pit stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.79,1:25:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,斯隆准备出发了\NSloan's ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.96,1:27:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  尼克\NHey, Nick!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.73,1:27:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\NNick!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.53,1:27:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\NOh. Nick!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.60,1:27:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  兄弟\NHey, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.43,1:27:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,和我谈谈  小伙子\NJust talk to me for a second, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.84,1:27:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让我失望  小子\NDon't disappoint me, boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.74,1:27:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你逮到我了\NYou got me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.94,1:27:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,和我谈谈\NTalk to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.64,1:27:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你欠我的  和我谈谈\NYou owe me that. Just talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.92,1:28:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们结婚时我告诉她\NI told her when we got married
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.79,1:28:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不必担心\Nthat she would not have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.46,1:28:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉她我会陪着她\NTold her I'd be there for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.49,1:28:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我那样保证了\NPromised.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.90,1:28:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我这辈子唯一真实的\NShe was the only real thing I had in this life.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.91,1:29:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,还是得逮捕你  尼克\NStill gonna have to take you in, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.16,1:29:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.59,1:29:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会去监狱\NI ain't going to prison.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.78,1:30:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你所做的我不怪你\NI don't blame you for what you done.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.72,1:30:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真的\NI don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.20,1:30:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但司法并不是你说了算\NBut justice isn't yours to serve.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.63,1:30:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是无人之境  尼克\NThis ain't the wild, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.50,1:30:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该让法律来处理\NYou should've let the law handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.18,1:30:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,法律不会像我这么做\NThe law wouldn't do what I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.24,1:30:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,法律是唯一让我们不变成野蛮人的东西\NLaw's the only thing keeps us from being savages.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.23,1:31:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,正如我所说  我不会去监狱\NLike I said, I can't go to prison,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.17,1:31:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,所以做你必须要做的\Nso you do whatever you gotta do.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.75,1:32:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉人们做这个镇的警察30年了\NI tell people I served this town for 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.02,1:32:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我的鲜血洒在这片土地上\NThat my blood is in this dirt.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.09,1:32:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在那段时间里\NAnd in all that time,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.80,1:32:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我只做了一件坏事\NI only ever did one bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.67,1:32:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想那么说\NIf you wanna call it that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.77,1:32:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,或许那是权力\NMaybe that's entitlement.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.81,1:32:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,或许不是\NMaybe not.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.05,1:32:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不管那是什么\NWhatever it is, though...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.89,1:32:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一个我可以承受的选择\N...it's a choice I can live with.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.07,1:32:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,想象一下如果他们放了参孙\NImagine if they let Samson go
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.41,1:33:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是把他关在寺庙里\Ninstead of shackling him to the temple.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.95,1:33:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也许结局就完全不一样\NMay have been a different outcome altogether.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.75,1:33:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,想想吧\NImagine that.
